&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuous professional development, product training, and career pathing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intradepartmental mentor and buddy program for in-house networking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An inclusive company culture, ability to join our Community Guilds (Datadog employee resource groups)&lt;/li&gt;
